# Atlas-app environment variables.
# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and adjust paths to match your local data.

# Path the dev/prod server uses to serve the PMTiles archive. Consumed by
# `getPmtilesPath()` in @atlasdraw/basemap/resolver.ts (Phase 4 T7).
# Must be reachable from the browser — i.e. an entry under `public/` or a
# volume-mounted route in production. Default `/data/world-low-zoom.pmtiles`
# matches the bundled archive shipped by `docker-compose.minimal.yml` (T10).
VITE_PMTILES_PATH=/data/world-low-zoom.pmtiles
